<br />
<br />I hacked up an Uncharted Waters and put the translated version of Just Breed on there. I also tapped one of pins of the MMC5 (pin 1,2 or 3, I can't remember), to get the extra sound channels.
<br />
<br />I'm not sure what other MMC5 carts have battery backup. Or I suppose you could hack up a real Just Breed cart.

		

